cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI 

The paper deals with handwritten paragraph recognition using neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model involves modifications to the architecture of the neural network, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the experiments involve databases and evaluation metrics commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
